SCHEMA: inspection/inspection_request.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.inspection.inspection_request
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define deterministic inspection request intent payload.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record inspection_request
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - request_id: id
    - requester_subject_id: id
    - target_kind: enum(structure|project|plan|node|manifest|cohort|faction|machine|port|graph|interior|interior_graph|interior_volume|interior_portal|pose_slot|mount_point)
    - target_id: id
    - desired_fidelity: enum(macro|meso|micro)
    - tick: int
    - max_cost_units: int
    - extensions: map
  optional:
    - time_range: map|null

INVARIANTS:
- max_cost_units must be non-negative.
- time_range, when provided, must satisfy start_tick <= end_tick.
